NAME

    Dancer2::Plugin::OpenAPI - OpenAPI plugin for Dancer2

    Please note that this module is not working and at the moment
    abandoned. Contact the author for more information.

VERSION

    Version 0.01

SYNOPSIS

    In your Dancer application:

        use Dancer2::Plugin::OpenAPI;

 openapi_operation

    Sets Dancer route for operation id $operation_id to subroutine
    $route_sub:

        openapi_operation showDancerById => sub {
            my $plugin = shift;
    
            $plugin->app->log(debug => 'showDancerById');
        };

